description: Application crashes when uploading large files over 500MB. Critical for daily operations.
resolution_notes: Updated file upload limits in configuration. Implemented chunked upload mechanism for large files.

description: Invoice shows incorrect pricing for additional users added mid-month.
resolution_notes: Corrected prorated billing calculation. Issued credit for overcharge. Updated billing system logic.

description: Multiple users unable to login after maintenance window. Business operations halted.
resolution_notes: Reset authentication tokens. Cleared cache on login servers. All users can now access system.

description: Request for dark mode theme option in user interface.
resolution_notes: Added to product roadmap for Q2 release. Provided workaround using browser extensions.

description: Data export function timing out for reports with more than 10000 records.
resolution_notes: Optimized database queries. Implemented background processing for large exports with email notification.

description: Salesforce integration stopped syncing contact data since last update.
resolution_notes: Identified API version compatibility issue. Updated integration endpoints and tested sync.

description: Dashboard loading very slowly, taking 30+ seconds to display analytics.
resolution_notes: Database indexing optimization. Implemented caching layer for frequently accessed data.

description: Forgot password reset email not being received.
resolution_notes: Email was in spam folder. Updated email templates and sender reputation configuration.

description: Need explanation of charges on latest invoice.
resolution_notes: Provided detailed breakdown of usage charges. Sent documentation on pricing structure.

description: API returning 500 errors for webhook endpoints affecting critical integrations.
resolution_notes: Server capacity issue during peak hours. Added load balancing and increased server resources.

description: Request for bulk user import functionality.
resolution_notes: Developed CSV import tool with validation. Beta testing with select customers before full release.

description: User permissions not working correctly after recent role changes.
resolution_notes: Permission cache issue. Cleared user session data and rebuilt permission matrix.

description: Mobile app slower than web version for same functions.
resolution_notes: Mobile app using older API endpoints. Updated to latest optimized API version.

description: Microsoft Teams integration not posting notifications correctly.
resolution_notes: Teams API rate limiting issue. Implemented retry logic and notification batching.

description: Search function returning incomplete results for certain keywords.
resolution_notes: Search index corruption. Rebuilt search index and updated indexing algorithm.

description: Urgent: Credit card payment failed, need immediate resolution to avoid service disruption.
resolution_notes: Payment processor temporary issue. Processed payment manually and updated auto-retry settings.

description: Cannot change email address in profile settings.
resolution_notes: UI bug preventing email updates. Fixed validation logic and deployed patch.

description: Request for keyboard shortcuts in main interface.
resolution_notes: Added common keyboard shortcuts. Updated help documentation with shortcut reference.

description: Database backup restoration needed after data corruption incident.
resolution_notes: Restored from daily backup taken 6 hours prior. Investigated root cause and strengthened data validation.

description: Report generation timing out for monthly analytics reports.
resolution_notes: Report complexity causing timeouts. Optimized queries and added progress indicators for long-running reports.

description: Zapier integration not triggering for certain events.
resolution_notes: Webhook delivery failures. Updated webhook retry logic and event filtering.

description: Discrepancy between usage dashboard and billing amounts.
resolution_notes: Billing calculation using old usage metrics. Updated billing system to match dashboard calculations.

description: Admin cannot access user management after security update.
resolution_notes: Security update changed admin permission structure. Updated admin role permissions.

description: Email notifications not being sent for certain system events.
resolution_notes: Email queue processing issue. Fixed queue worker and implemented monitoring alerts.

description: Request for single sign-on (SSO) integration with Azure AD.
resolution_notes: Implemented SAML-based SSO. Conducted testing with customer's Azure AD environment.

description: Page refresh required to see updated data in real-time views.
resolution_notes: WebSocket connection issues. Updated real-time sync mechanism and connection handling.

description: Google Analytics integration showing incorrect conversion data.
resolution_notes: Analytics tracking code outdated. Updated to GA4 implementation and verified data accuracy.

description: Two-factor authentication setup failing for multiple users.
resolution_notes: 2FA service provider API changes. Updated authentication flow to handle new API requirements.

description: Question about upgrade pricing and feature differences.
resolution_notes: Provided detailed comparison chart. Scheduled demo call to review pro features.

description: Critical system outage affecting all users during peak hours.
resolution_notes: Load balancer failure during traffic spike. Implemented redundant load balancers and auto-scaling.

description: Request for custom branding options in reports.
resolution_notes: Added logo upload and color customization options. Updated report templates accordingly.

description: Slow query performance affecting dashboard load times.
resolution_notes: Database optimization and query restructuring. Added performance monitoring for ongoing optimization.

description: Slack integration commands not responding correctly.
resolution_notes: Slack API token expired. Updated token management system with automatic renewal.

description: Profile picture upload not working in account settings.
resolution_notes: File size validation too restrictive. Updated image processing to handle various formats and sizes.

description: Billing dispute - charged for users that were deactivated last month.
resolution_notes: Identified billing system delay in processing deactivations. Issued refund and fixed timing issue.

description: Data visualization charts not rendering correctly in Chrome browser.
resolution_notes: Browser compatibility issue with chart library. Updated to latest version with Chrome fixes.

description: Request for advanced filtering options in data tables.
resolution_notes: Implemented multi-column filtering with date ranges and custom operators.

description: System becomes unresponsive during daily backup process.
resolution_notes: Backup process using too many system resources. Moved to off-peak hours and optimized process.

description: HubSpot contact sync creating duplicate entries.
resolution_notes: Duplicate detection logic not working for contacts with similar names. Enhanced matching algorithm.

description: Users unable to reset passwords using security questions.
resolution_notes: Security question validation too strict. Updated validation logic and improved error messages.

description: Mobile app notification badges not updating correctly.
resolution_notes: Push notification service configuration issue. Updated notification handling and badge counting.

description: Auto-renewal notification not received before billing.
resolution_notes: Email notification system missing renewal reminders. Implemented 30/15/7 day reminder sequence.

description: Urgent request for audit trail functionality for compliance requirements.
resolution_notes: Developed comprehensive audit logging system. Implemented user action tracking and export capabilities.

description: Large file uploads failing intermittently.
resolution_notes: Network timeout issues with large files. Implemented chunked upload with resume capability.

description: Webhook endpoints timing out causing integration failures.
resolution_notes: Increased webhook timeout limits. Implemented async processing for webhook handlers.

description: Cannot update company information in account profile.
resolution_notes: Form validation preventing updates with certain characters. Fixed validation regex patterns.

description: Session timeout occurring too frequently during active use.
resolution_notes: Session management too aggressive. Extended timeout for active users and improved activity detection.

description: Need invoice in different currency for accounting requirements.
resolution_notes: Added multi-currency invoice generation. Configured automatic currency conversion based on location.

description: Request for automated data backup scheduling options.
resolution_notes: Implemented flexible backup scheduling with multiple frequency options and retention policies.

description: Critical performance degradation during month-end processing.
resolution_notes: Resource contention during batch processing. Implemented queue management and resource allocation.
